{"tid":1220744,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[每日一犬] 支持連登仔每日重點認識新犬隻","createTime":"2019-06-14T05:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T06:41:52.000Z","uid":71004,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"744d8f8ecce22773d4f5926c93c9af6af1eb25a0","tid":1220744,"uid":71004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:19:02.000Z","msg":"狗係人類最好嘅朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到近日巴打們傾囊分享咗唔少佢地認識嘅狗 頓時發覺連登有愛 原來大家都鍾意狗狗 特別係黑犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為動物愛好者嘅我當然係想藉此機會深入認識新狗狗 俾佢地知道人類對佢地嘅關懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我覺得單單收集狗狗資料係唔夠嘅, 因為呢d 唔夠針對性嘅行動 <br />\n好容易做成錯覺 令呢班狗狗以為大家知完就算 唔會將心中愛嘅實踐 從而感到備受冷落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以啊 我覺得要發起每日一犬 每日介紹一隻狗狗作為重點關愛對象<br />\n集結連登仔嘅力量 話俾佢地知人間有愛 做狗路上永不孤單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最重要係教識佢地一個道理<br />\n善惡到頭終有報 只爭來早與來遲 <br />\n<br />\n請問大家支唔支持<br />\n支持請 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對請 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38298c71c93ee605602175397681a93534b6de17","tid":1220744,"uid":52230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:31:01.000Z","msg":"等我做警犬第一血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ba414b01b20961c2d92178860ff58676f77c1c","tid":1220744,"uid":71004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38298c71c93ee605602175397681a93534b6de17","tid":1220744,"uid":52230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:31:01.000Z","msg":"等我做警犬第一血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:39:16.000Z","msg":"恭喜恭喜"},{"pid":"9c9bc1a62461bf5013a02508a2cdb8ce42ee293b","tid":1220744,"uid":71004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80cc4b6677ea8e649c8cda9c4e77ed85768111c8","tid":1220744,"uid":71004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:08:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09397b5ead8b8a545856e781024e4c8fc9ae7701","tid":1220744,"uid":71004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"推"}]}